title: Black Up-Pointing Double Triangle

nouns: A mark to indicate a direction or relation
A mark to indicate a direction or relation.
A sign or symbol used to indicate a direction (e.g. \to).

description: Two triangles pointing up. Similar to rewind icon, rotated 90° clockwise.
apple_vendor_description: The fast-forward button on Apple devices is rendered as a sleek, geometric arrow pointing upwards, conveying a sense of rapid ascent and progress. Its design features Apple's signature glossy 3D shading, with subtle highlights and shadows that give it a polished, tactile feel. This emoji on Apple devices is commonly used to signify moving forward quickly, skipping ahead, or achieving a goal with speed and efficiency.
